Usage:

  rails generate neo4j:scaffold model_name [property:type, property:type]

Description:

  Scaffolds a Neo4j resource from model to controller, views and routes. The 
  resource is ready to use as a starting point for your Neo4jr based application.

  Attribute pairs define property names type should be property for the standard types
  supported by Neo4j e.g. string

  If you want to remove all the generated files, run

      'rails destroy neo4j:scaffold ModelName'

Example:

    `rails generate neo4j:scaffold purchase order_id:integer amount:decimal`